&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 class="relative group">यावत् जीवामः तावदेव मनुष्यस्य शरीरस्य महत्वं भवति
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE-%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5-%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B5-%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE-%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5-%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B5-%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>पूर्वम् एकः महान् राजा आसीत्!&lt;br>
सः बहु धर्मिष्ठः आसीत्!&lt;/p>
